<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Issue Status Updated - Carbon Cube Kenya</title>
  </head>

  <body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; background-color: #f9fafb; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <div style="max-width: 620px; margin: 30px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
      <div style="background: #1f2937; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 25px 20px;">
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 10px; width: 100%;">
          <div style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle;">
            <img src="https://carboncube-ke.com/logo.png" alt="Carbon Cube Kenya" style="height: 50px; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 8px;" />
            <span style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; letter-spacing: 1px; vertical-align: middle;">ARBONCUBE</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af;">Kenya's Most Trusted Online Marketplace</p>
      </div>
      
      <div style="padding: 30px 25px;">
        <h1 style="color: #111827; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 24px;">ðŸ“¢ Issue Status Update</h1>

        <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Hi <strong><%= @user_name %></strong>,</p>

        <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
          We have an update on your issue! The status has been changed and we wanted to keep you informed.
        </p>

        <div style="background: #f0f9ff; border: 1px solid #bae6fd; padding: 18px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center;">
          <h3 style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #0369a1; text-align: left;">Status Update</h3>
          <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; gap: 15px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin: 15px 0;">
            <span style="background: #fff3cd; color: #856404; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase;"><%= @old_status %></span>
            <span style="font-size: 20px; color: #666;">â†’</span>
            <span style="background: <% case @issue.status when 'in_progress' %>#d1ecf1<% when 'completed' %>#d4edda<% when 'closed' %>#d6d8db<% when 'rejected' %>#f8d7da<% else %>#fff3cd<% end %>; color: <% case @issue.status when 'in_progress' %>#0c5460<% when 'completed' %>#155724<% when 'closed' %>#383d41<% when 'rejected' %>#721c24<% else %>#856404<% end %>; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase;"><%= @new_status %></span>
          </div>
          <p style="margin: 15px 0 0 0; color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
            Updated on <%= @updated_at %>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div style="background: #f9fafb; padding: 18px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 15px; color: #374151; text-align: center;">
          <h3 style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #111827;">What this means:</h3>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-style: italic; color: #6b7280;"><%= @status_message %></p>
        </div>

        <div style="background: #f0f9ff; border: 1px solid #bae6fd; padding: 18px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
          <h3 style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #0369a1; text-align: left;">ðŸ“‹ Issue Details</h3>
          <p><strong>Issue Number:</strong> <span style="color: #0369a1; font-weight: 600;">#<%= @issue_number %></span></p>
          <p><strong>Title:</strong> <%= @issue_title %></p>
          <p><strong>Current Status:</strong> 
            <span style="background: <% case @issue.status when 'in_progress' %>#d1ecf1<% when 'completed' %>#d4edda<% when 'closed' %>#d6d8db<% when 'rejected' %>#f8d7da<% else %>#fff3cd<% end %>; color: <% case @issue.status when 'in_progress' %>#0c5460<% when 'completed' %>#155724<% when 'closed' %>#383d41<% when 'rejected' %>#721c24<% else %>#856404<% end %>; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase;"><%= @new_status %></span>
          </p>
          <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> <%= @updated_at %></p>
        </div>

        <% if @issue.status == 'completed' %>
          <div style="background: #d4edda; border: 1px solid #c3e6cb; border-radius: 8px; padding: 18px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center;">
            <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #155724; font-size: 16px;">ðŸŽ‰ Issue Resolved!</h4>
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #155724;">Thank you for reporting this issue. Your feedback helps us improve our platform for everyone.</p>
          </div>
        <% end %>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 25px 0;">
          <a href="<%= @tracking_url %>" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: #fbbf24; color: #111827; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px;">View Issue Details</a>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: #374151;">If you have any questions about this update or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>

        <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 25px; color: #374151;">Best regards,<br>
        <strong>The Carbon Cube Kenya Team</strong></p>

        <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 25px 0;">
        <p style="font-size: 10px; color: #6b7280;">
          This email was sent to <%= @issue.reporter_email %>. 
          If you have any questions, please contact us at +254 712 990 524.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div style="background: #f9fafb; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
          <img src="https://carboncube-ke.com/logo.png" alt="Carbon Cube Kenya" style="height: 25px; width: 25px; opacity: 0.7;" />
        </div>
        <p><strong>Carbon Cube Kenya</strong> | 9th Floor, CMS Africa, Nairobi</p>
        <p>Phone: +254 712 990 524 | Email: <%= ENV['BREVO_EMAIL'] %></p>
        <p>Â© 2025 Carbon Cube Kenya. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
